ground-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-ba9c03cc-6db3-4af6-8b7f-9f3bb071d55f\">2024년에도 더욱 진심을 다해 진료하는 이수한의원이 되겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-06f9dce5-6d06-4485-ab9c-1bdbda24d6b0\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-f8077cdc-8978-4bd5-893e-6297e10c15fb\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-d800a9cf-3f93-45bb-9417-5f15de9f80c4\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-3f1c83e3-b7fa-41ed-8567-00e1e139767b\">감사합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>    </div>",
